# Overriding these numbers will force PingDirectory to produce duplicate server IDs if not fully tested.
# As of now PD_POD_LIMIT_INDEX=1000 and PD_BASE_DN_LIMIT_INDEX=20 will allow up to 50 pingdirectory pods per cluster with up to 11
# 11 backends/base_dns.
